summary: This document is a declaration by Ren Nathan, a custodian of records for Southwest Airlines Co., certifying the authenticity of records provided in response to a subpoena issued by the Assistant United States Attorney. The declaration affirms that the records were created in the regular course of business and are accurate.

persons.name: Ren Nathan
persons.context: Ren Nathan is the declarant who certifies the authenticity of the records provided in response to a subpoena.

keyFacts: Ren Nathan is the custodian of records for Southwest Airlines Co.
The declaration was executed on January 29, 2020.
The document certifies the authenticity of records in response to a subpoena from the Assistant United States Attorney.
The records were made in the regular course of business and are claimed to be accurate.
